metadata.name: CASCADIA Jan 15 2021 Michael Martini
metadata.description: In the winter of 2021 I asked friends to try to enter a random sequence of values between 0 and 9, each keystroke adding one pixel to the image until 10,000 pixels were added to the 100x100 canvas. Michael's production was visibly different from mine, and from this Proof of Work was born.
